PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1778429470
OL,3,CFive party contests see Conservatives
OL,4,Cand Labour lose grip on southern
OL,5,Ccouncils
OL,7,FThe verdict from voters had been
OL,8,Fstored up since 2021, when all seats
OL,9,Fwere last up for grabs on our county
OL,10,Fcouncils.
OL,12,FThat was a political lifetime ago,
OL,13,Fwhen Boris Johnson was Tory leader and
OL,14,Fprime minister, and doing well in the
OL,15,Fopinion polls as the coronavirus
OL,16,Fvaccine was rolled out.
OL,18,FIn West Sussex the Lib Dems surged to
OL,19,Fthe front of the pack, while just one
OL,20,Fseat now separates them from the
OL,21,FTories in Hampshire.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
