OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1778429470
OL,3,CFive party contests see Conservatives
OL,4,Cand Labour lose grip on southern
OL,5,Ccouncils
OL,7,FWhile the Tories got a kicking in
OL,8,Ftheir traditional rural county
OL,9,Fauthorities, Labour lost their grip on
OL,10,Fseveral other local councils.
OL,12,FThe Labour leader of Southampton City
OL,13,FCouncil suffered the embarrassment of
OL,14,Flosing his council seat as his party
OL,15,Fslipped back and was deprived of its
OL,16,Fmajority.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
