OL,3,CFive party contests see Conservatives
OL,4,Cand Labour lose grip on southern
OL,5,Ccouncils
OL,7,FSouthampton Itchen MP Darren Paffey
OL,8,Fdescribed the result as "really
OL,9,Fdifficult" and said his thoughts were
OL,10,Fwith "decent and hardworking
OL,11,Fcouncillors" who lost their seats.
