OL,3,CFive party contests see Conservatives
OL,4,Cand Labour lose grip on southern
OL,5,Ccouncils
OL,7,FLabour also lost control of Worthing
OL,8,FBorough Council, on the Sussex coast,
OL,9,Fwhich slipped to 'no overall control'
OL,10,Fwith Green and Reform gains a
OL,11,Ffortnight after a visit from Nigel
OL,12,FFarage.
OL,14,FSir Keir Starmer's party held onto
OL,15,Fneighbouring Adur District Council,
OL,16,Fdespite Reform gains, but couldn't
OL,17,Fwrestle back control of Hastings
OL,18,FBorough Council from the Greens ` who
OL,19,Fconverted their minority into a
OL,20,Fmajority.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
