OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1778429470
OL,3,CFive party contests see Conservatives
OL,4,Cand Labour lose grip on southern
OL,5,Ccouncils
OL,7,FThat illustrated the myriad of
OL,8,Felectoral challenges for the
OL,9,Ftraditional big two parties in the
OL,10,FSouth East.
OL,12,FThe Conservatives are shedding seats
OL,13,Fto the Lib Dems in parts of West
OL,14,FSussex and Hampshire, and to Reform
OL,15,Fand the Greens in East Sussex.
OL,17,FWhile Labour also faces a three-
OL,18,Fpronged pincer in many of its
OL,19,Fhistorical centres of support in our
OL,20,Fregion's towns and cities.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1778429470
OL,3,CFive party contests see Conservatives
OL,4,Cand Labour lose grip on southern
OL,5,Ccouncils
OL,7,FWhile there were glimmers of hope `
OL,8,FLabour kept Reading and the Tories
OL,9,Fheld Fareham ` it was clear they were
OL,10,Fboth the big losers.
OL,12,FIt has seen a number of local
OL,13,Fauthorities falling to 'no overall
OL,14,Fcontrol' at a time when council
OL,15,Fleaders are meant to be preparing for
OL,16,Fthe biggest shake-up of local
OL,17,Fgovernment for a generation.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1778429470
OL,3,CFive party contests see Conservatives
OL,4,Cand Labour lose grip on southern
OL,5,Ccouncils
OL,7,FThat means many of these newly elected
OL,8,Fcouncillors will only serve a two-year
OL,9,Fterm before their authorities, and
OL,10,Fwith it their role, is consigned to
OL,11,Fthe history books.
OL,13,FMany political scientists will be
OL,14,Fconsidering where these local
OL,15,Felections have confirmed that the two-
OL,16,Fparty system is already a thing of the
OL,17,Fpast.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
